"House of the Dark Shadows"
(Episode 10)

19
00:01:58,828 --> 00:02:01,289
My Lord only spends time with Ms. Malai,

20
00:02:01,445 --> 00:02:03,835
don't you think I will be lonely?

21
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:06,156
I am aware that

22
00:02:06,766 --> 00:02:07,906
what I ask of you

23
00:02:07,914 --> 00:02:09,101
is not a small request,

24
00:02:09,688 --> 00:02:10,843
And I'm not belittling you,

25
00:02:10,867 --> 00:02:11,867
but...

26
00:02:12,359 --> 00:02:13,476
But what, my lord?

27
00:02:13,641 --> 00:02:14,694
You damn Bu-nga!

28
00:02:16,883 --> 00:02:18,070
Having your own wife

29
00:02:18,086 --> 00:02:19,203
sleeping with another man,

30
00:02:19,227 --> 00:02:20,227
shameful!

31
00:02:20,266 --> 00:02:21,101
Malai!

32
00:02:21,117 --> 00:02:22,265
Never hang out with

33
00:02:22,281 --> 00:02:23,375
that kind of person again!

34
00:02:23,922 --> 00:02:24,922
Watch out, ma'am!

35
00:02:31,688 --> 00:02:32,804
Could it be that

36
00:02:33,187 --> 00:02:34,867
you are in a hurry to tend

37
00:02:34,906 --> 00:02:35,750
to your lover?

38
00:02:35,775 --> 00:02:37,148
- How dare you?
- No, Fueang.

39
00:02:46,348 --> 00:02:47,769
You dare slap me, you damn Malai?

40
00:02:47,778 --> 00:02:48,660
Indeed!

41
00:02:48,684 --> 00:02:50,152
I'm willing to waste my energy

42
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,144
to slap your face

43
00:02:51,184 --> 00:02:52,410
and teach you that

44
00:02:52,707 --> 00:02:53,882
if you live in a house,

45
00:02:54,262 --> 00:02:56,855
cease barking like a
stray dog on the street.

46
00:02:57,278 --> 00:02:58,472
I will tell the viscount

47
00:02:58,488 --> 00:02:59,629
that you slapped me!

48
00:02:59,653 --> 00:03:01,316
I will ensure that you
will pay. Just watch!

49
00:03:01,341 --> 00:03:02,590
Do as you wish.

50
00:03:03,231 --> 00:03:04,402
The Viscount will learn

51
00:03:04,427 --> 00:03:05,918
what kind of person you are

52
00:03:06,332 --> 00:03:08,043
that made me resort to such action.

53
00:03:08,598 --> 00:03:09,355
Fueang.

54
00:03:09,387 --> 00:03:10,910
- Yes, ma'am?
- Fetch me a cloth.

55
00:03:11,848 --> 00:03:12,848
Yes, ma'am.

56
00:03:16,551 --> 00:03:17,551
Here you go, ma'am.

57
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:29,879
Oh.

58
00:03:30,558 --> 00:03:32,175
Wiping dirt from her hands.

59
00:03:33,465 --> 00:03:35,011
Fueang, you...

60
00:03:36,941 --> 00:03:37,893
Let us leave, Fueang.

61
00:03:41,414 --> 00:03:42,734
The audacity!

62
00:03:43,289 --> 00:03:44,367
Come back here!

63
00:03:44,391 --> 00:03:45,960
Cowards, look...

64
00:03:47,328 --> 00:03:48,328
Chaem!

65
00:03:48,539 --> 00:03:49,664
How could you allow

66
00:03:49,672 --> 00:03:50,742
this to happen to me?

67
00:03:50,969 --> 00:03:53,351
Why did you just stand there silently?

68
00:03:54,406 --> 00:03:55,859
I apologize, Ms. Ramphoei,

69
00:03:56,211 --> 00:03:56,976
well...

70
00:03:57,016 --> 00:03:58,216
I was afraid.

71
00:03:58,734 --> 00:03:59,796
If she finds out that

72
00:03:59,805 --> 00:04:01,531
I let the snake loose in her room,

73
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,750
it will all be over.

74
00:04:05,828 --> 00:04:06,710
Coward!

75
00:04:06,742 --> 00:04:07,750
It's not like she can

76
00:04:07,766 --> 00:04:08,819
just smell your hands.

77
00:04:08,844 --> 00:04:10,352
Why should you be afraid?

78
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:12,515
The more you act this way,

79
00:04:12,867 --> 00:04:14,171
the more suspicious she'll become.

80
00:04:14,844 --> 00:04:15,844
Fool!

81
00:04:16,195 --> 00:04:17,304
My apologies, ma'am.

82
00:04:17,781 --> 00:04:18,781
From now on,

83
00:04:19,211 --> 00:04:20,944
I won't be afraid anymore.

84
00:04:22,218 --> 00:04:23,218
Please forgive me.

85
00:04:23,766 --> 00:04:24,710
Good!

86
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:25,992
From now on,

87
00:04:26,016 --> 00:04:27,406
try to protect me

88
00:04:27,422 --> 00:04:29,523
like how Fueang protects Malai!

89
00:04:29,563 --> 00:04:30,390
Got it?

90
00:04:30,406 --> 00:04:31,846
Yes, I understand.

91
00:04:31,852 --> 00:04:32,852
Go!

92
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,000
Where to?

93
00:04:34,117 --> 00:04:35,281
To see the viscount!

94
00:04:35,664 --> 00:04:37,530
I will not be slapped in vain!

95
00:04:37,883 --> 00:04:39,563
- Depart!
- Yes, ma'am.

96
00:04:44,612 --> 00:04:45,806
What is it, Ramphoei?

97
00:04:45,815 --> 00:04:46,806
Why did you come here?

98
00:04:50,135 --> 00:04:51,361
My lord...

99
00:04:52,221 --> 00:04:54,416
It's Malai, my lord.

100
00:04:54,674 --> 00:04:56,431
I don't know what's wrong with her.

101
00:04:56,455 --> 00:04:57,111
Oww...

102
00:04:57,135 --> 00:04:59,408
She suddenly attacked me.

103
00:05:00,026 --> 00:05:02,806
Behold, my cheeks are all red.

104
00:05:03,924 --> 00:05:04,924
Ouch...

105
00:05:05,979 --> 00:05:08,361
Malai attacked you?

106
00:05:09,049 --> 00:05:10,549
Since being with Malai,

107
00:05:10,807 --> 00:05:13,197
she has not dared to harm even a fly.

108
00:05:13,799 --> 00:05:14,799
But, my lord,

109
00:05:14,815 --> 00:05:16,080
Ms. Ramphoei speaks the truth.

110
00:05:16,127 --> 00:05:17,736
I witnessed it with my own eyes.

111
00:05:17,761 --> 00:05:18,800
Even if Malai did it,

112
00:05:18,825 --> 00:05:19,777
there must be a reason.

113
00:05:20,401 --> 00:05:22,017
Just don't disturb Malai again,

114
00:05:22,042 --> 00:05:23,722
that would be enough.

115
00:05:24,330 --> 00:05:26,845
My lord, are you not concerned about me?

116
00:05:26,870 --> 00:05:28,970
Will you not approach her on my behalf?

117
00:05:31,893 --> 00:05:32,947
If so,

118
00:05:32,956 --> 00:05:34,940
you probably wouldn't be angry either

119
00:05:35,385 --> 00:05:36,760
if Ms. Malai

120
00:05:37,151 --> 00:05:38,557
has

121
00:05:38,838 --> 00:05:39,838
an affair.

122
00:05:42,088 --> 00:05:43,940
What? What affair?

123
00:05:44,588 --> 00:05:46,682
I do not understand what you are saying.

124
00:05:47,331 --> 00:05:48,736
If you are here to speak nonsense,

125
00:05:48,745 --> 00:05:49,541
leave.

126
00:05:49,549 --> 00:05:50,713
I have work to attend to.

127
00:05:52,557 --> 00:05:53,557
Viscount!

128
00:05:53,635 --> 00:05:55,338
You are glorify your primary wife

129
00:05:55,363 --> 00:05:56,636
too fervently, my lord!

130
00:05:56,838 --> 00:05:58,760
Ms. Malai is having an affair with Dech.

131
00:05:58,784 --> 00:06:00,518
Will you not take any action, my lord?

132
00:06:00,768 --> 00:06:01,182
Hey.

133
00:06:01,487 --> 00:06:02,557
Oww, my lord!

134
00:06:02,628 --> 00:06:03,705
Cease it, Ramphoei!

135
00:06:03,931 --> 00:06:06,198
When did Dech become Malai's lover?

136
00:06:06,393 --> 00:06:07,768
You are not making any sense.

137
00:06:07,823 --> 00:06:09,623
I'm not spouting nonsense.

138
00:06:09,674 --> 00:06:10,838
The proof is how Dech

139
00:06:10,846 --> 00:06:12,096
got bitten by a snake.

140
00:06:12,307 --> 00:06:13,713
The servants say

141
00:06:13,815 --> 00:06:16,908
he was bitten in Ms. Malai's bedroom.

142
00:06:17,112 --> 00:06:19,268
The evidence is so obvious.

143
00:06:21,096 --> 00:06:22,104
I now comprehend

144
00:06:22,666 --> 00:06:25,065
why Malai attacked Ramphoei.

145
00:06:25,729 --> 00:06:27,377
You said that to her, right?

146
00:06:27,776 --> 00:06:29,174
What of it, my lord?

147
00:06:29,331 --> 00:06:30,611
It is the truth!

148
00:06:30,799 --> 00:06:32,479
Cease spreading lies.

149
00:06:32,791 --> 00:06:33,846
Dech went in to change

150
00:06:33,862 --> 00:06:34,916
the lightbulbs for me.

151
00:06:34,941 --> 00:06:36,791
He did nothing of the sort to Malai.

152
00:06:38,003 --> 00:06:39,096
If you persist in coming up

153
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,752
with unfounded accusations against her,

154
00:06:40,784 --> 00:06:42,033
next time, I will not only chase you

155
00:06:42,065 --> 00:06:42,995
out of the room,

156
00:06:43,019 --> 00:06:44,580
but out of the house!

157
00:06:44,713 --> 00:06:45,236
Leave!

158
00:06:52,983 --> 00:06:54,295
What are you staring at?

159
00:06:54,303 --> 00:06:54,990
Just leave!

160
00:06:54,998 --> 00:06:56,358
Oh, yes, my lord.

161
00:07:01,748 --> 00:07:02,482
Let us leave, ma'am.

162
00:07:05,553 --> 00:07:07,021
The viscount will be upset!

163
00:07:09,467 --> 00:07:11,248
What is wrong with this household?

164
00:07:11,756 --> 00:07:13,467
Stay calm, ma'am. Let's return.

165
00:07:13,492 --> 00:07:14,154
Chaem.

166
00:07:14,163 --> 00:07:14,850
Huh?

167
00:07:14,866 --> 00:07:16,306
Remember my words,

168
00:07:16,538 --> 00:07:18,568
Malai shall not be living joyously.

169
00:07:18,991 --> 00:07:20,670
As long as I still draw breath,

170
00:07:21,186 --> 00:07:22,670
one of us must perish,

171
00:07:23,116 --> 00:07:24,053
be it me or her.

172
00:07:25,787 --> 00:07:26,959
But it has to be her

173
00:07:27,397 --> 00:07:28,397
that dies.

174
00:07:36,277 --> 00:07:37,292
Please wait for me.

175
00:07:43,550 --> 00:07:45,815
I must devise a plan to keep those two

176
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,907
away from Ramphoei's scrutiny.

177
00:07:50,668 --> 00:07:52,206
Ramphoei is excessively meddlesome.

178
00:08:10,796 --> 00:08:12,139
Has he been in such a state

179
00:08:12,155 --> 00:08:13,147
since last night?

180
00:08:13,296 --> 00:08:14,303
Yes, Ms. Malai.

181
00:08:15,312 --> 00:08:16,678
Last night, the viscount stayed

182
00:08:16,694 --> 00:08:18,358
to observe his condition until morning,

183
00:08:18,374 --> 00:08:19,389
and then left.

184
00:08:22,124 --> 00:08:23,124
Ms. Malai.

185
00:08:23,444 --> 00:08:24,678
Allow me to do it.

186
00:08:25,577 --> 00:08:26,670
It's alright.

187
00:08:27,053 --> 00:08:28,162
Please attend to your duties

188
00:08:28,187 --> 00:08:28,928
if you have any.

189
00:08:28,968 --> 00:08:30,256
I'll tend to Dech myself.

190
00:08:30,437 --> 00:08:31,694
- But...
- Go on.

191
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:35,600
As you wish, ma'am.

192
00:08:35,757 --> 00:08:37,522
But I'll come back

193
00:08:37,538 --> 00:08:39,397
in case people with loose tongues

194
00:08:39,422 --> 00:08:41,222
saw you and gossip about you again.

195
00:08:42,568 --> 00:08:43,497
Let them be.

196
00:08:44,036 --> 00:08:45,886
They can think whatever they want.

197
00:08:47,779 --> 00:08:48,779
Yes, ma'am.

198
00:09:04,762 --> 00:09:05,957
It shouldn't have been you.

199
00:09:07,973 --> 00:09:10,440
The one deserving to be bitten is me.

200
00:09:32,413 --> 00:09:33,413
Ms. Malai.

201
00:09:33,921 --> 00:09:36,240
I fell in love with you since then,

202
00:09:36,858 --> 00:09:38,045
even though I knew

203
00:09:38,382 --> 00:09:39,936
I would never see you again.

204
00:09:40,374 --> 00:09:41,576
Ms. Malai of my heart.

205
00:09:43,108 --> 00:09:47,967
(House of the Dark Shadows
novel: Phakhinai, screenplay: Wannason)

206
00:09:48,061 --> 00:09:53,061
(House of the Dark Shadows
novel: Phakhinai, screenplay: Wannason)

207
00:10:04,050 --> 00:10:05,050
Ms. Malai.

208
00:10:06,768 --> 00:10:07,877
You are awake.

209
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:10,550
Yes, ma'am.

210
00:10:11,401 --> 00:10:13,260
Do any parts of your body still hurt?

211
00:10:13,893 --> 00:10:14,854
Do you want water?

212
00:10:14,878 --> 00:10:15,924
I will fetch it for you.

213
00:10:19,245 --> 00:10:20,385
It's alright, ma'am.

214
00:10:22,089 --> 00:10:24,112
Just having Ms. Malai taking care of me

215
00:10:25,245 --> 00:10:27,299
has already blessed me greatly.

216
00:10:27,940 --> 00:10:29,190
What blessing?

217
00:10:30,479 --> 00:10:32,221
You shouldn't have gotten bitten

218
00:10:32,246 --> 00:10:33,705
by the snake instead of me.

219
00:10:34,393 --> 00:10:35,979
Why did you do that, Dech?

220
00:10:36,323 --> 00:10:37,799
You should have just let me

221
00:10:37,823 --> 00:10:38,752
get bitten and die.

222
00:10:38,768 --> 00:10:40,729
Please do not say such thing, Ms. Malai.

223
00:10:45,490 --> 00:10:46,896
Ms. Malai, do you still

224
00:10:46,921 --> 00:10:49,178
remember the day we first met?

225
00:10:56,451 --> 00:10:57,521
I remember.

226
00:11:01,849 --> 00:11:04,802
That day was the saddest day of my life.

227
00:11:08,218 --> 00:11:09,554
I can never forget it.

228
00:11:11,984 --> 00:11:13,859
We are bound by blood, elder brother.

229
00:11:14,891 --> 00:11:16,242
Why do you cast me aside

230
00:11:16,267 --> 00:11:18,039
as if I were a mere swine or cur?

231
00:11:18,813 --> 00:11:20,813
You are not my sole sibling.

232
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,835
Should you seek refuge with me,

233
00:11:22,852 --> 00:11:24,382
won't others follow suit?

234
00:11:24,407 --> 00:11:25,735
You are a human.

235
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:27,727
It'd be a disgrace if you can't survive.

236
00:11:28,781 --> 00:11:29,781
Brother...

237
00:12:07,211 --> 00:12:08,125
Lady!

238
00:12:11,094 --> 00:12:12,008
Lady!

239
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:14,594
Lady!

240
00:12:15,290 --> 00:12:16,204
Lady!

241
00:12:16,610 --> 00:12:17,524
Lady!

242
00:12:17,938 --> 00:12:19,281
What are you doing, lady?

243
00:12:19,555 --> 00:12:20,555
Huh?

244
00:12:21,219 --> 00:12:22,133
Lady.

245
00:12:22,688 --> 00:12:24,688
- I wish to die!
- Lady!

246
00:12:24,713 --> 00:12:26,531
I wish to die! Let go!

247
00:12:27,211 --> 00:12:28,125
Lady...

248
00:12:28,898 --> 00:12:29,827
Let go!

249
00:12:29,852 --> 00:12:30,445
Lady.

250
00:12:30,461 --> 00:12:31,581
I wish to die!

251
00:12:31,602 --> 00:12:32,492
Please calm down.

252
00:12:32,797 --> 00:12:33,445
Lady.

253
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:41,800
I wish to die!

254
00:12:43,126 --> 00:12:43,774
Lady.

255
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,133
Please come and sit, lady.

256
00:13:05,954 --> 00:13:07,992
If not, then I shall go sit over there.

257
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:10,672
It's alright.

258
00:13:11,352 --> 00:13:13,008
I do not wish to inconvenience you.

259
00:13:13,024 --> 00:13:14,024
Please sit.

260
00:13:33,572 --> 00:13:36,673
People's sorrows are like rain.

261
00:13:37,908 --> 00:13:40,033
They come and they go.

262
00:13:42,332 --> 00:13:44,418
Whatever troubles your heart now,

263
00:13:46,543 --> 00:13:49,199
I believe it will pass soon.

264
00:13:50,215 --> 00:13:51,863
All that is needed is patience.

265
00:13:53,926 --> 00:13:55,504
Have you ever heard that

266
00:13:56,231 --> 00:13:57,793
the skies after rain

267
00:13:58,167 --> 00:13:59,347
are always beautiful?

268
00:14:06,785 --> 00:14:07,785
I suppose

269
00:14:09,183 --> 00:14:10,573
mine is

270
00:14:11,761 --> 00:14:13,281
more like a storm.

271
00:14:15,644 --> 00:14:17,331
I do not know when it will end.

272
00:14:46,722 --> 00:14:47,722
Thank you

273
00:14:48,511 --> 00:14:49,964
for taking the trouble

274
00:14:49,972 --> 00:14:51,308
to light a fire to warm me.

275
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:53,714
I did it for myself as well.

276
00:14:54,347 --> 00:14:55,534
No need to thank me.

277
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:01,221
I hope thy sorrows lift soon.

278
00:15:02,088 --> 00:15:03,682
Even storms fade away.

279
00:15:04,307 --> 00:15:06,104
Your worries shall fade away too.

280
00:15:07,706 --> 00:15:10,385
Just as the sun is sure to shine again,

281
00:15:11,151 --> 00:15:12,736
as long as you don't lose hope,

282
00:15:13,049 --> 00:15:14,221
there will always be chances

283
00:15:14,229 --> 00:15:15,338
for new beginnings.

284
00:15:16,112 --> 00:15:17,150
I believe so.

