403
00:24:09,371 --> 00:24:10,441
You know, my lord,

404
00:24:10,465 --> 00:24:12,222
even if you forbid me,

405
00:24:12,269 --> 00:24:14,120
I will follow you there.

406
00:24:14,316 --> 00:24:15,589
Don't believe me? Just watch.

407
00:24:32,478 --> 00:24:33,665
Tell me what you want

408
00:24:33,689 --> 00:24:34,923
