443
00:26:30,041 --> 00:26:31,081
Yes, my lord.

444
00:26:43,765 --> 00:26:44,890
It's a pity that

445
00:26:44,929 --> 00:26:46,350
I couldn't catch the person

446
00:26:46,390 --> 00:26:47,670
who harmed you, Ramphoei.

447
00:26:47,781 --> 00:26:48,694
That's true, my lord.

448
00:26:48,718 --> 00:26:50,015
If I could catch them,

449
00:26:50,038 --> 00:26:52,572
I would make them suffer tremendously!

450
00:26:52,820 --> 00:26:54,530
How dare they harm my master.

451
00:26:59,663 --> 00:27:01,077
My lord,

452
00:27:01,421 --> 00:27:02,663
I'm in so much pain like this,

453
00:27:02,679 --> 00:27:03,921
