455
00:27:05,742 --> 00:27:06,624
Of course not.

456
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:07,640
I have made arrangements.

457
00:27:07,656 --> 00:27:08,804
How could I not go?

458
00:27:09,101 --> 00:27:11,468
You have Chaem to take care of you here.

459
00:27:11,835 --> 00:27:13,343
I will be back in just a few days,

460
00:27:13,374 --> 00:27:15,233
