487
00:28:19,755 --> 00:28:21,278
Take care of her well, Chaem.

488
00:28:21,653 --> 00:28:23,778
Let me know if anything is lacking.

489
00:28:24,107 --> 00:28:25,356
Yes, my lord.

490
00:28:37,257 --> 00:28:38,843
