500
00:29:00,976 --> 00:29:02,507
There are still many ways

501
00:29:02,717 --> 00:29:03,997
to obstruct her.

502
00:29:11,066 --> 00:29:12,480
Why are you here, Saeng?

503
00:29:12,746 --> 00:29:14,534
Something concerning the servant abode?

504
00:29:16,324 --> 00:29:17,605
No, my lord.

505
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:19,581
I merely wanted to see

506
00:29:19,606 --> 00:29:21,231
the face of a heartless person.

507
00:29:21,464 --> 00:29:22,964
