519
00:29:49,005 --> 00:29:50,605
to hurt Ms. Ramphoei

520
00:29:51,651 --> 00:29:52,885
in order to prevent her

521
00:29:52,910 --> 00:29:54,526
from hindering you at Hua Hin.

522
00:29:55,183 --> 00:29:57,151
