565
00:32:41,108 --> 00:32:43,631
but listening to it makes me sad.

566
00:32:44,327 --> 00:32:45,701
Makes me wonder whether

567
00:32:45,725 --> 00:32:46,936
the musician is suffering.

568
00:32:48,280 --> 00:32:49,826
I'm not suffering or anything.

569
00:32:50,007 --> 00:32:51,687
You're just spouting nonsense.

570
00:32:54,741 --> 00:32:56,674
I thought you were suffering,

571
00:32:57,030 --> 00:32:58,194
given that the viscount

572
00:32:58,219 --> 00:32:59,506
is dragging you to Hua Hin,

573
00:32:59,538 --> 00:33:00,873
having barely recovered.

574
00:33:02,593 --> 00:33:04,553
There are many servants in the abode,

575
00:33:05,218 --> 00:33:07,022
why did he choose you specifically?

576
00:33:07,296 --> 00:33:08,592
He also doesn't allow me

577
00:33:08,600 --> 00:33:09,686
to follow Ms. Malai,

578
00:33:09,710 --> 00:33:10,710
so strange.

579
00:33:12,303 --> 00:33:13,342
It's not strange.

580
00:33:13,843 --> 00:33:15,928
The viscount must have needed my help.

581
00:33:16,827 --> 00:33:18,256
Or do you wish to witness.

582
00:33:18,702 --> 00:33:20,084
Saeng become the favored servant

583
00:33:20,109 --> 00:33:20,983
instead of me?

584
00:33:21,014 --> 00:33:21,983
Ugh.

585
00:33:22,327 --> 00:33:23,334
No way,

586
00:33:23,897 --> 00:33:25,381
it's better if it's you.

587
00:33:25,577 --> 00:33:26,600
Were it Saeng,

588
00:33:26,616 --> 00:33:28,030
he would strut about the house

589
00:33:28,055 --> 00:33:29,484
in a vainglorious manner.

590
00:33:31,600 --> 00:33:33,701
The viscount's trip to Hua Hin this time

591
00:33:33,858 --> 00:33:35,458
may bring good news,

592
00:33:35,968 --> 00:33:37,209
your mistress Ms. Malai

593
00:33:37,218 --> 00:33:38,287
will be at ease too.

594
00:33:41,129 --> 00:33:42,168
True,

595
00:33:43,247 --> 00:33:44,660
but part of me doesn't want

596
00:33:44,668 --> 00:33:45,902
the viscount to have a child,

597
00:33:45,911 --> 00:33:47,629
that he may relinquish power,

598
00:33:47,637 --> 00:33:49,512
and finally granting us liberty.

599
00:33:51,942 --> 00:33:54,535
You think too simply Fueang,

600
00:33:54,926 --> 00:33:56,332
the liberty you speak of

601
00:33:56,598 --> 00:33:58,049
would prove more arduous

602
00:33:58,074 --> 00:33:59,457
than our service here.

603
00:34:00,114 --> 00:34:01,121
I'm fine with that.

604
00:34:04,549 --> 00:34:07,033
As long as I have you by my side,

605
00:34:07,159 --> 00:34:09,331
I fear no difficulties.

606
00:34:10,363 --> 00:34:11,565
Should we escape,

607
00:34:12,495 --> 00:34:14,182
we could live together.

608
00:34:14,230 --> 00:34:15,230
Please, Dech?

609
00:34:15,378 --> 00:34:17,378
Please, Dech?

610
00:34:18,527 --> 00:34:19,581
Very well.

611
00:34:19,980 --> 00:34:21,050
If we can break free,

612
00:34:21,066 --> 00:34:22,237
I will live with you

613
00:34:23,011 --> 00:34:24,940
and care for you like a real sister.

614
00:34:30,714 --> 00:34:32,800
You've always been like a sister to me

615
00:34:33,152 --> 00:34:34,205
and I'll cherish

616
00:34:34,230 --> 00:34:35,573
you as a sister forever.

617
00:34:36,464 --> 00:34:38,197
Do you understand, Fueang?

618
00:34:39,503 --> 00:34:40,503
Yeah.

619
00:34:45,862 --> 00:34:46,807
I'll take my leave.

620
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:16,502
Chaem, come and help me.

621
00:35:17,291 --> 00:35:19,158
Take it slow, Ms. Ramphoei.

622
00:35:23,748 --> 00:35:24,748
Hey!

623
00:35:26,147 --> 00:35:27,232
How did you get in here?

624
00:35:27,264 --> 00:35:28,373
And where is Chaem?

625
00:35:28,545 --> 00:35:29,662
She went downstairs

626
00:35:29,678 --> 00:35:31,076
to fetch your breakfast,

627
00:35:31,491 --> 00:35:33,240
so I came to stand in for her.

628
00:35:34,569 --> 00:35:35,881
And where is the viscount?

629
00:35:35,913 --> 00:35:37,225
Why don't I see him?

630
00:35:37,264 --> 00:35:38,623
The viscount went to Hua Hin

631
00:35:38,639 --> 00:35:40,381
with Ms. Mali since dawn, ma'am.

632
00:35:40,467 --> 00:35:41,467
What?

633
00:35:43,155 --> 00:35:44,155
How come?

634
00:35:44,357 --> 00:35:45,615
The viscount went without

635
00:35:45,640 --> 00:35:46,646
saying goodbye to me.

636
00:35:46,858 --> 00:35:48,410
I think the viscount probably

637
00:35:48,427 --> 00:35:50,043
didn't want to disturb your rest, ma'am.

638
00:35:50,748 --> 00:35:51,928
Besides,

639
00:35:52,131 --> 00:35:53,537
he probably doesn't want to suffer

640
00:35:53,545 --> 00:35:54,967
through someone's incessant chatter

641
00:35:54,975 --> 00:35:56,779
and ruin his mood before departing.

642
00:35:57,959 --> 00:35:58,959
Uan!

643
00:36:00,420 --> 00:36:01,803
In this condition,

644
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:03,467
it would be a burden

645
00:36:03,475 --> 00:36:04,529
if you tag along, ma'am.

646
00:36:04,538 --> 00:36:05,787
You were just attacked

647
00:36:05,811 --> 00:36:06,912
and soaked in blood.

648
00:36:07,098 --> 00:36:08,341
I don't believe you will

649
00:36:08,366 --> 00:36:09,521
die easily, ma'am.

650
00:36:11,068 --> 00:36:12,209
Uan!

651
00:36:12,217 --> 00:36:13,217
Oww...

652
00:36:13,592 --> 00:36:14,935
Cease this, Ms. Ramphoei.

653
00:36:15,288 --> 00:36:16,771
Or everyone will know discover that

654
00:36:16,788 --> 00:36:17,834
you're as tough as

655
00:36:17,859 --> 00:36:18,882
any other servants here.

656
00:36:19,108 --> 00:36:20,318
You're only lying down

657
00:36:20,827 --> 00:36:22,267
to gain sympathy.

658
00:36:24,662 --> 00:36:25,803
Uan! Ah!

659
00:36:26,178 --> 00:36:26,881
Oww...

660
00:36:26,905 --> 00:36:27,967
Your origin

661
00:36:28,569 --> 00:36:29,850
is no different from me.

662
00:36:30,795 --> 00:36:31,865
You are not worthy enough

663
00:36:31,881 --> 00:36:33,146
for the viscount to bid farewell.

664
00:36:33,420 --> 00:36:34,435
Remember that!

665
00:36:40,010 --> 00:36:41,158
Why, you little...!

666
00:36:41,370 --> 00:36:42,370
Ouch!

667
00:36:51,018 --> 00:36:52,924
I know not what you are thinking,

668
00:36:53,378 --> 00:36:54,877
but following after the viscount

669
00:36:54,901 --> 00:36:56,932
now will surely incur his anger, ma'am.

670
00:36:57,003 --> 00:36:58,596
What I do is my own business,

671
00:36:59,323 --> 00:37:00,869
no need to stick your nose in.

672
00:37:01,042 --> 00:37:02,562
I'm merely worried.

673
00:37:03,104 --> 00:37:04,658
Ms. Ramphoei is still injured.

674
00:37:05,104 --> 00:37:06,385
Following the viscount now

675
00:37:06,409 --> 00:37:07,502
would be dangerous.

676
00:37:07,534 --> 00:37:09,158
I have my own ways,

677
00:37:10,143 --> 00:37:11,518
no need for concern, Saeng.

678
00:37:12,003 --> 00:37:13,123
You may leave.

679
00:37:14,846 --> 00:37:15,846
Yes, ma'am.

680
00:37:21,885 --> 00:37:25,486
(Hua Hin House)

681
00:37:26,323 --> 00:37:27,455
Hurry and go now,

682
00:37:27,463 --> 00:37:28,963
so you wouldn't reach there late.

683
00:37:29,065 --> 00:37:30,065
Ramphoei,

684
00:37:30,385 --> 00:37:31,604
don't forget that

685
00:37:31,784 --> 00:37:32,984
I'm still on the run.

686
00:37:33,409 --> 00:37:34,409
Geez.

687
00:37:34,729 --> 00:37:36,268
You've been on the run for so long.

688
00:37:36,293 --> 00:37:38,150
What are you afraid of at this point?

689
00:37:39,143 --> 00:37:40,455
Even you

690
00:37:40,628 --> 00:37:42,916
were attacked in broad daylight.

691
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:46,894
I find this to be so suspicious.

692
00:37:47,690 --> 00:37:50,338
I don't care how suspicious it is.

693
00:37:50,721 --> 00:37:52,500
I want you to kill that Malai woman

694
00:37:52,525 --> 00:37:54,580
and end this matter once and for all.

695
00:37:55,995 --> 00:37:56,995
Kill her?

696
00:37:59,221 --> 00:38:00,096
No more rape?

697
00:38:00,135 --> 00:38:01,260
I've changed my mind.

698
00:38:01,285 --> 00:38:02,744
I don't want to keep her around

699
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:04,088
like a snake in the grass.

700
00:38:04,112 --> 00:38:06,080
Even though she won't suffer that much.

701
00:38:06,105 --> 00:38:07,175
Should have gone with this

702
00:38:07,183 --> 00:38:08,214
from the beginning.

703
00:38:08,230 --> 00:38:09,555
Then it wouldn't be so troublesome.

704
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:10,580
Brother,

705
00:38:10,604 --> 00:38:12,424
there are only a few people over there.

706
00:38:12,432 --> 00:38:13,775
When you return,

707
00:38:13,807 --> 00:38:15,369
I hope to hear good news.

708
00:38:16,167 --> 00:38:17,713
Believe in me, Ramphoei.

709
00:39:03,396 --> 00:39:05,083
You never think of loving others

710
00:39:05,099 --> 00:39:06,536
except for yourself, my lord!

711
00:39:06,552 --> 00:39:07,364
Dech!

712
00:39:07,380 --> 00:39:08,380
My lord!

713
00:39:12,521 --> 00:39:14,755
The woman just now is your mother?

714
00:39:15,037 --> 00:39:16,153
Yes, her name is Fueang.

715
00:39:16,162 --> 00:39:17,380
If you don't wish to die,

716
00:39:17,405 --> 00:39:19,435
do not get involved with that house!

717
00:39:23,123 --> 00:39:24,950
That's not true, it was just a dream.

718
00:39:25,380 --> 00:39:26,630
How could it be real?

719
00:39:43,872 --> 00:39:49,432
♪ Here's a heart
that's always faithful ♪

720
00:39:49,692 --> 00:39:53,816
♪ Ready to be given
to you for good ♪

721
00:39:55,398 --> 00:40:01,232
♪ Here's a life
that's still being offered ♪

722
00:40:01,969 --> 00:40:05,486
♪ To you alone ♪

723
00:40:05,657 --> 00:40:11,463
♪ You might be unaware
and still wondering ♪

724
00:40:11,703 --> 00:40:17,736
♪ Why I'm willing to do
everything for you ♪

725
00:40:18,325 --> 00:40:20,776
♪ Whatever you want ♪

726
00:40:21,212 --> 00:40:25,856
♪ Everything I've done ♪

727
00:40:26,213 --> 00:40:28,496
♪ What's it for? ♪

728
00:40:28,599 --> 00:40:33,949
♪ I can't give you my reasons ♪

729
00:40:34,518 --> 00:40:39,936
♪ Love has its own reason ♪

730
00:40:40,238 --> 00:40:45,736
♪ I've only done
what my heart wants ♪

731
00:40:46,053 --> 00:40:51,816
♪ All you have to do
is accept my love ♪
